有難うねいつもお疲れ様

Even in an era where indies are coming out with retro-3D graphics, a game like CoH really shows its age. Character faces are a flat texture, and hands are big oven mitts.
The game also has an older structure, where leveling is very much part of the core experience.
I love it, but hard to recommend.
